근데 정리하면 &lt;/p></description></item><item><title>세상에서 가장 작은 32bit ARM Microcontroller</title><link>https://openmicrolab.com/%EC%84%B8%EC%83%81%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EA%B0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%9E%91%EC%9D%80-32bit-arm-microcontroller/</link><pubDate>Mon, 31 Jan 2011 05:02:49 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://openmicrolab.com/%EC%84%B8%EC%83%81%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EA%B0%80%EC%9E%A5%EC%9E%91%EC%9D%80-32bit-arm-microcontroller/</guid><description>
